          <li><strong>Commercial-Style Range Igniters</strong> — KitchenAid's KFGC and KFCC Commercial-Style ranges use a different igniter configuration than standard ranges. The dual-stacked burner assembly requires specific OEM igniters — generic ones fail quickly at the higher heat output. We keep these on the truck.</li>
          <li><strong>EPA-Certified Sealed System Work</strong> — KitchenAid refrigerators with compressor or sealed-system failures require EPA-certified technicians. We carry the equipment and certification for refrigerant work — compressor replacements, sealed system leaks, and refrigerant recharge.</li>
